{"tid":660648,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"水貨客被劫百萬人民幣","createTime":"2018-05-11T01:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T03:50:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7ffaca535a8372ce4ff75ceffa8fcd01bf57f693","tid":660648,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T01:09:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180511/20387331?_ga=2.236949895.703613058.1525914001-1183266771.1516234590\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180511%2F20387331%3F_ga%3D2.236949895.703613058.1525914001-1183266771.1516234590&d=E3UvubJckY66CQjiX2yg4NZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=a67a4a36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180511%2F20387331%3F_ga%3D2.236949895.703613058.1525914001-1183266771.1516234590&h=61e9fc25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180511/20387331?_ga=2.236949895.703613058.1525914001-1183266771.1516234590</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月11日 <br />\n<br />\n水貨客被劫百萬人民幣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180511/large/11lp9p03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180511%2Flarge%2F11lp9p03.jpg&h=345cb3e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警員撿走遺在馬路上的手機保護殼調查。張家豪攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名水貨客昨午帶着100萬元人民幣（約124萬港元）由深圳經落馬洲管制站返港，在落馬洲皇巴站對開巴士站準備搭車離去時，遭3名蒙面賊人搶去載有該筆巨款的背囊，事主為保巨款反抗，被賊人推跌地上，手部擦傷。3名賊人得手後挾贓乘客貨車逃去，警方接報採取捷進行動追截賊車無果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三賊夾擊得手逃去<br />\n<br />\n遇劫事主姓陳（48歲），據悉他從事水貨生意，當時正準備攜巨款往交收，警方初步調查後，懷疑賊人早有預謀，洞悉事主身懷巨款，配備車輛埋伏附近伺機搶劫，邊界警區重案組正循線追緝涉案客貨車及賊人。<br />\n現場落馬洲青山公路新田段公共運輸交匯處皇巴站對開巴士站，昨下午近3時半，<br />\n事主由深圳經皇崗及落馬洲管制站返港，他攜着載有100萬元人民幣的背囊步往巴士站，準備登乘一輛駛往天水圍天慈的B1線巴士時，一名賊人突然從後出現，並企圖搶走他的背囊，事主反抗與賊人糾纏；此時另兩名賊人出現，其中一人將他推跌地上令其手機墮地保護殼甩脫，另一人藉機搶去背囊，然後與兩同黨乘接應客貨車向元朗逃去。事主手部擦傷，事後報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張家豪、徐雲庭  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n台北殺人案　港男或加控<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n灣仔沙中綫地盤又現炸彈拆彈需時更長　警指封路延續至今天日間"},{"pid":"bc7c5e173da852e4dcaf5be8e5915a13e8a4c505","tid":660648,"uid":35014,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T01:10:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0ffbb905e41bf04601fdb0836bdf63bf4df84ba","tid":660648,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T01:13:26.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"966809aafe217a607cff8b1a21ede717ddd67c42","tid":660648,"uid":185258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T01:14:44.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"d39dc0b79f88c9bcdfe43005e140663ef9a36ffc","tid":660648,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T01:18:54.000Z","msg":"走私,唔係水貨"},{"pid":"430d994eb5257a1673b19f2c29836a517fab6c60","tid":660648,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T01:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec83770d8ef1ca09fa9c6cb0a3760f36b3cc114","tid":660648,"uid":166413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T01:24:26.000Z","msg":"咁洗唔洗陪"},{"pid":"758928932fe88fd220d4a3875c64c4b11d44d034","tid":660648,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T01:28:03.000Z","msg":"螞蟻搬家"},{"pid":"64a5753e1d84f160c9b927f727c110ed9a609b93","tid":660648,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T01:36:49.000Z","msg":"贏呀"},{"pid":"c140f637662732845e5c3a59703091d7ac30abb7","tid":660648,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T01:36:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>人嚟 笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\